{"type": "article", "id": 16907, "title": "Tori系列椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-02T06:50:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122437MzdnjLJhbAwNZYt9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是斯洛伐克设计师 Tomas Kral 推出的“Tori（鸟居）”椅子系列，模拟了日本建筑中石牌坊、竖石纪念碑和鸟居等木石材质的建筑。座位下面都有一个像梁一样的结构，四只腿也是圆柱形的，有优雅而古典的气质。鸟居在日本传统中是灵魂休憩的地方，这一系列的椅子也有类似的象征。<a href=\"http://www.tomaskral.ch/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是工作室主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261441412kEmMiAQJC6wvNuK.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144142GLfbNcpEJUaF427Q.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"654\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261441428M2iFrvtfSdLbejX.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"655\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8007335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144143dQksDgv7NlH0XOG6.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}